com.mobius.vdrapi
Interface IEnhancedSearchTopicItemResult

All Known Implementing Classes:
EnhancedSearchTopicItemNode
public interface IEnhancedSearchTopicItemResult

A class implements IEnhancedSearchTopicItemResult to indicate that it is a result of a EnhancedSearchTopicItemFactory createList call.

This interface is similar to ISearchTopicItemResult without inner data container classes. All data access is made through get methods.

Method Summary

          Returns the document locator & archive status information that corresponds to this single node.

          Returns the report information that corresponds to this single node.
